The paper discusses the formal analysis of a cryptographic protocol, specifically the Secure Remote Password (SRP) protocol. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also mentions the use of the Cryptographic Protocol Shapes Analyzer (CPSA), which falls under the category of formal methods in computer science. This suggests that the paper could also belong to categories such as cs.CY (Computational Geometry), cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), cs.IT (Information Theory), and cs.SE (Software Engineering). However, since the focus of the paper is on cryptography and security, cs.CR is the most likely category.
